{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/gethwid"]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Type Method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)getHWID","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"getHWID","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getHWID"}],"title":"getHWID"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/getHWID","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Returns the Pushwoosh Hardware ID (HWID) for this device.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getHWID"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The unique Pushwoosh device identifier (never nil)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The HWID is a unique device identifier used in all Pushwoosh API calls and for device tracking","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in the Pushwoosh Control Panel. On iOS, this is derived from "},{"code":"UIDevice.identifierForVendor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The HWID remains consistent across app launches and is used to:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Identify the device in the Pushwoosh Control Panel","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Track user behavior and engagement","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Target specific devices for push notifications"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Link devices to user accounts in your backend"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sync device with your backend for cross-platform user tracking:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class DeviceRegistrationService {","","    func registerDeviceWithBackend(userId: String) {","        let hwid = Pushwoosh.configure.getHWID()","        let pushToken = Pushwoosh.configure.getPushToken()","","        let deviceInfo: [String: Any] = [","            \"hwid\": hwid,","            \"userId\": userId,","            \"pushToken\": pushToken ?? \"\",","            \"platform\": \"ios\",","            \"appVersion\": Bundle.main.appVersion,","            \"osVersion\": UIDevice.current.systemVersion","        ]","","        APIClient.shared.post(\"\/api\/devices\/register\", body: deviceInfo) { result in","            switch result {","            case .success:","                Logger.info(\"Device registered with backend: \\(hwid)\")","            case .failure(let error):","                Logger.error(\"Device registration failed: \\(error)\")","            }","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It may change if the user reinstalls all apps from the same vendor.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/getHWID":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/getHWID","title":"getHWID","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"getHWID","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns the Pushwoosh Hardware ID (HWID) for this device."}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getHWID"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/gethwid","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","kind":"symbol","title":"PushwooshCore","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","role":"collection"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","title":"PWConfiguration"}}}